    "text": "Wednesday, 22 July - A Total Solar Eclipse in Wuhan",
    "emoji": "🌑",
    "children": [
      {
        "id": "p1",
        "text": "Today was an amazing day.",
        "emoji": "✨",
        "keywords": "amazing, day",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p1_1",
            "text": "There was a total solar eclipse in Wuhan!",
            "emoji": "🌞",
            "keywords": "total, solar, eclipse",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p1_2",
            "text": "I woke up early because I couldn't wait to see it!",
            "emoji": "⏰",
            "keywords": "early, wait",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p2",
        "text": "My friends and I went down to the Yangtze River to find a good place to watch it.",
        "emoji": "🌊",
        "keywords": "Yangtze, River, watch",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p2_1",
            "text": "We took cameras, chairs, food and drink, and special glasses so we could look at it.",
            "emoji": "🕶️",
            "keywords": "cameras, special glasses",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p2_2",
            "text": "Lots of people gathered there to watch too.",
            "emoji": "👨‍👩‍👧‍👦",
            "keywords": "people, gathered",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p3",
        "text": "Slowly, the moon moved in front of the sun.",
        "emoji": "🌓",
        "keywords": "moon, sun",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p3_1",
            "text": "It looked like someone bit a hole in the sun!",
            "emoji": "🍩",
            "keywords": "hole, sun",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p3_2",
            "text": "It got darker and darker as the moon slowly covered the sun.",
            "emoji": "🌘",
            "keywords": "darker, covered",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p4",
        "text": "At 9:26 a.m. the moon completely covered the sun.",
        "emoji": "🌚",
        "keywords": "9:26, completely",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p4_1",
            "text": "The sky went dark.",
            "emoji": "🌌",
            "keywords": "sky, dark",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p4_2",
            "text": "The crowd gasped and cheered.",
            "emoji": "🙌",
            "keywords": "gasped, cheered",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p5",
        "text": "The light of the sun made a ring of light around the moon.",
        "emoji": "💍",
        "keywords": "ring, light",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p5_1",
            "text": "The total eclipse lasted for over five minutes!",
            "emoji": "⏱️",
            "keywords": "five, minutes",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p6",
        "text": "In the afternoon, I spent hours reading about astronomers, eclipses, and how the planets move in our solar system.",
        "emoji": "📚",
        "keywords": "reading, astronomers, planets",
        "children": [
          {
            "id": "p6_1",
            "text": "The universe is simply amazing!",
            "emoji": "🌌",
            "keywords": "universe, amazing",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "id": "p6_2",
            "text": "I also watched some videos with famous Chinese astronauts.",
            "emoji": "👩‍🚀",
            "keywords": "Chinese, astronauts",
            "children": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "id": "p7",
        "text": "I want to become an astronaut or astronomer someday too.",
        "emoji": "🔭",
        "keywords": "become, astronaut",
        "children": [
